properties.property:
The teachings of the Yellow Father are wicked and dangerous.
His apprentices hate whatever brings pleasure and joy in life. They view the material realm as irredeemable hell, and the body as an impure prison of flesh.
To punish their bodies, they wear exoskeletons which, like iron maidens, cause constant physical pain.
They hate life, and yet they are forbidden from escaping it on their own. That makes them fearless warriors who seek death in battle.
You must be as fearless as them if you wish to succeed.
You might ask: why would anyone decide to take this path?
Many people in the galaxy are so miserable that they would trade physical suffering for some sense of purpose and belonging.
